<date id="6446100CFFBEFFFCFAB32DFBFA89FE29" box="[1296,1382,476,501]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" value="1956-10-30">56 x 30</date>
µm) with two-four riblets in upper half of ventral side of scale.
</paragraph>
